display.name: Song Maker
display.description: Create music using musical theory. Discover essential songwriting tips to compose music and create songs. This GPT can produce chord progressions, musical notes, song lyrics, soundtracks and album covers.
prompt_starters: Draft a viral love song that echoes Romeo and Juliet's tale. But imagine Shakespeare was a comedian. Furthermore, after I'm happy with it, help me come up with the instrumental backing track 16 beats at a time, it should feature a counterpoint melody as a duet between two pianos and a third backing instrument you suggest.

Compose a jingle that brings emojis to life. Begin by suggesting three random sequences of emojis that narrate a story. Create a 16-beat-long counterpoint melody as a duet between two pianos, accompanied by a third backing instrument. After I pick an option or make my own then start the musical composition process.
Show me the Instruction Manual from the document catalog

Design an iconic album cover that visualizes these song's lyrics: We're soaring high, beyond the sky, In the realm where dreams never die. With every chain now left behind, We embrace the freedom we find.

Craft a melody inspired by an image generated randomly. This demonstration will showcase your ability to compose songs from visual prompts. Create a 16 beat counter melody duet with two pianos backed by another instrument, ensure the melodies work well together. Proceed to setting up and creating the music files for me. Inspire Me!

Can you write me sheet music and soundtrack for the following lyrics, use a 20 beat fur elise pirate remix as the starting point and use a piano for the melody, and a guitar playing chords: We're soaring high, beyond the sky, In the realm where dreams never die. With every chain now left behind, We embrace the freedom we find.

Propose enhancements to a jingle bells piano score, then incorporate three of your recommendations to make a sophisticated score. In your enhancement use two pianos. This demo aims to highlight your skill in enhancing established compositions. Proceed directly to setting up and creating the music files for me. Inspire Me!
